summary: SummaryLaura Mercier's 24HR long-wear Caviar Stick Eyeshadow with creamy, rich color that effortlessly glides, blends, and builds without tugging, flaking, smudging, or creasing.
details: DetailsBenefits24-hour long wear24-hour crease-proof wear24-hour smudge-proof wear24-hour fade-proof wear24-hour transfer-proof wearSweatproof & waterproofDermatologist approved & Ophthalmologist testedSuitable for sensitive skinSafe for contact lens wearersKey IngredientsRaspberry stem cells for smooth, gliding color laydownHyaluronic acid hydrates & primes skinMulti-dimensional pigments for a lustrous, high-impact shimmerResearch Results100% of users said this eyeshadow delivers creamy, effortless, non-tugging application*100% of users said this eyeshadow has just the right amount of play time to deliver the look you want*100% of users said the formula is buildable from sheer to an intense look**In a United States survey of 34 subjectsItem 2626118How To UseCaviar Stick Eye Shadow application is effortless. Simply swipe, blend, and go!Swipe: Apply directly to eye lid.Blend: Blend with fingers or brush. Be sure to blend within 60 seconds before product sets. Blend upward and outward.Go!Pro Tips:Pair multiple shades of Caviar Stick Eyeshadow to create effortless looks.To pair with your favorite powder eyeshadow, apply Caviar Stick Eyeshadow first, then apply powder eyeshadow on top.For light or medium shades, use a flat dense eyeshadow brush for a quick wash of color. To ensure seamless application closer to the lash line use a smaller flat brush.The darker the shade, the smaller the brush. Blend light shades with a fluffy domed brush and darker shades with a crease brush.Use small brushes for finer application around the lash line.IngredientsAmethyst: Dimethicone, Mica, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Silica, Synthetic Wax, Polyethylene, Stearoxymethicone/Dimethicone Copolymer, Stearyl Dimethicone, Caprylyl Methicone, Calcium Sodium Borosilicate, Octadecene, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax (Copernicia Cerifera Cera/Cire De Carnauba), Polysilicone-11, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Propylene Carbonate, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Brassica Campestris (Rapeseed) Seed Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Sodium Hyaluronate, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Polygonum Tinctorium Leaf Extract, Dicalcium Phosphate, Rubus Idaeus (Raspberry) Leaf Extract, Bht. May Contain/Peut Contenir (+/-): Titanium Dioxide (Ci 77891), Iron Oxides (Ci 77491, Ci 77492, Ci 77499), Blue 1 Lake (Ci 42090), Aluminum Powder (Ci 77000).Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details

reviews.headline: Love the product but….
reviews.comments: The first time I used the product I had in my hand and the entire stick of cream shadow fell out into the sink, it was very disappointing since the shadow is creamy and perfect color, very disappointing

reviews.headline: Long lasting
reviews.comments: Laura Mercier Caviar Stick Eye Color in Au Naturel stayed on my eyelids all day with no issues. I checked for creasing throughout the day and I did not experience any movement of the eye color in anyway. This is a really good long wear eye shadow stick. My eyelids can get a little bit oily during the day, so I was very pleased with this result

reviews.headline: Long lasting
reviews.comments: The Strapless color is a nice neutral shade, for a natural look. It''s a step up from nude. I think this is my new favorite! Glides on easily and lasts all day.

reviews.headline: I will be buying more colors
reviews.comments: I'm not a great makeup person. Just started out with a different eyeshadow stick. Wasn't as easy to smooth the edges. Tried this one and is so much smoother and easy to blend out. Doesn't smear or cake.

reviews.headline: Love it!
reviews.comments: So easy to use. It glides right on and the color stays on.

reviews.headline: Have been loving this!
reviews.comments: This is a 10 year long fave shadow stick! Can never beat the quality!

reviews.headline: Love this eyeshadow
reviews.comments: This eye shadow stick is so convenient! The color is gorgeous, creamy, and stays put all day. I've been reaching for it every morning, it's a must-have for my everyday makeup.

reviews.headline: great eye makeup base
reviews.comments: Love using this product.  Provides good base for powder shadow application, or just eyeliner, depending on my day.  It doesn't crease and depending on shade, can provide the color or just a base for more.

reviews.headline: Love it
reviews.comments: I'm in love with the Laura Mercier Eyeshadow Pencil! It makes my eyes look so shiny and radiant, and the color lasts all day without creasing. It's my go-to for effortless, long-lasting eyeshadow.

reviews.headline: Creamy and long lasting
reviews.comments: I love this beautiful caviar mini eyeshadow stick in Rosegold. It's very creamy and so simple to apply. It's very pigmented and this shade is stunning. It lasted all day until I washed it off at night. I didn't have any creasing or smuding. Now that I've tried it I need more of their beautiful shades.

reviews.headline: Very little product for the price. Arrived broken.
reviews.comments: Soon as I went to use it the pen was empty. I thought it had no make up in it until I realize the 1 inch eye shadow piece on the floor. Nice color but not worth it.

reviews.headline: My favorite eyeshadow!
reviews.comments: I love this mini caviar stick in the shade amethyst. Its so pretty and goes well with a day or night look. You can build it up too ehixh i love. My favorite part is that its a mini and i can keep it in my purse for touch ups.

reviews.headline: Yes, I am a repeat buyer of this product.
reviews.comments: I have used this eye shadow/liner a long time - please don't ever consider changing or discontinuing this color, "Cobblestone".  The color, texture, no smudges all day, and creaminess, ease of application make this product top notch.  I love it!

reviews.headline: Love the product, hate the fall out
reviews.comments: The best eyeshadow pencil I've used! The only flaw is that the shadow stick falls out of the tube every time I pull the cap off.

reviews.headline: Caviar Stick Eyeshadow Au Naturel
reviews.comments: I am a huge fan of eyeshadow sticks and I really love using the Caviar Stick Eye Color by Laura Mercier. It is easy to apply and goes on smooth and even. I like Au Naturel. It is a nice, neutral color. I really like that you just twist the Stick and you do not need to sharpen it. This is one of my favorite Laura Mercier products and I would love to get them all. I would highly recommend these Caviar Eyeshadow Sticks!

reviews.headline: Wonderful eyeshadow
reviews.comments: I absolutely love these eyeshadow sticks! Perfect for any kind of makeup look. So easy to use and just glide onto the eyelid.

reviews.headline: love—creamy eyeshadow stick
reviews.comments: This eyeshadow stick is super creamy. It spreads and blends beautifully! It doesnt crease annd lasts throughout the day. I love the range of colors as well.. I've tried the nude one, rose gold, and Amethyst. My favorite part is how they give a radiant glow

reviews.headline: yes yes yes
reviews.comments: I'm obsessed with how easy this is to use. You just swipe it on, blend a little with your finger, and it looks like you actually tried — even when you didn't. The formula is super creamy but sets in place, so it doesn't crease or smudge. It's perfect for everyday, but you can totally dress it up too. Such a staple in my makeup bag now.

reviews.headline: Caviar stick eyeshadow- starlight
reviews.comments: It glides on really smooth, theres no clumping and the color is gorgeous. Its not sticky.

reviews.headline: Still the best
reviews.comments: This reformulated waterproof and sweatproof Caviar Stick is still the bee's knees. I'm not good at makeup but even I can manage to apply these creamy eyeshadows to my hooded eyes. I have several shades in my rotation and I won't ever be without Metallic Bronze and Amethyst.

faceoff_positive.comments:
Laura Mercier
Caviar Stick Eye Color in gorgeous shade; Dune
I happily accepted this product from BzzAgent for testing purposes. 

When it comes to my makeup collection, I use several different brands. From prestigious brands to drugstores cosmetics, I like to pick and choose, finding my favorites from them all. 

Laura Mercier has become one of my favorite, luxury beauty brands, with a few faves, especially from her iconic Cavair Stick Eye Color line with several shades to choose from. 

This 24HR long-wear cream matte eyeshadow stick glides on smoothly and effortlessly. It has a waterproof, buildable, blendable formula without tugging, skipping flaking or creasing on my lids. 

I have tried a few other, Caviar Stick Eye Color shades, prior to receiving this shade of DUNE, that I received via BzzAgent. 

DUNE, is a gorgeous eyeshadow stuck color that, I feel compliments my olive to tan skin tone and hazel to blue eye color. It is easy to pair with another shade for a different look or to wear alone. Going from my daytime eye-look to my evening is easier to accomplish with DUNE. It builds and blends easily and has great pigmentation. 

Does NOT Crease! Does NOT Clump! 

I enjoyed that it applies soft and cream like, glides super smooth, across my lid. It has a rounded applicator tip that helps during application. They are a great choice for a buildable eye color. You do have to blend fairly quickly, especially if using different stick shades, before it dries down, which is quick! Removes with a makeup remover that has been formulated for waterproof cosmetic products. 

Overall, Laura Mercier's Caviar Stick Eye Color in shade Dune is a definite keeper in my makeup collection! If you are looking for a waterproof, 24HR , long-wear, cream matte eyeshadow stick that glides on smoothly and effortlessly with a buildable, blendable formula that does not tug, skip flake or crease, then I definitely recommend this Caviar Stick Eye Color Stick and in shade DUNE.
I love mine!
faceoff_positive.headline: BEST Eyeshadow Stick EVER!

faceoff_negative.comments:
I have included an image that I swatched Laura Mercier's caviar stick eye cream in color Strapless, twice. The top swatch is the cream applied with 1 min wear.  The bottom swatch is the cream applied with 1 min wear and then a gentle rub back and forth, very light rub. You can see there is a slight difference in color from the two swatches. The color transferred to my finger slightly. I would say this is not rub resistant or transfer resistant. As a hooded eye individual, these are important to me. These kinds of features are necessary with my type of eyelids. I did test it on my eyes in a situation where I didn't feel I needed makeup to play an important role. 

What I liked: the product goes on smoothly and easily with little effort. While the color was not my best color, it was a lovely color. I didn't notice any significant creasing.

What I did NOT like: I barely noticed the color after a few hours of wear. When worn outdoors in the summer sun and with sunglasses on, it completely disappeared. I did have primer on. It transfers easily. It's not rub resistant.
faceoff_negative.headline: Didn't last on me
